lead_paragraph: Chelsea fans will always have a place in their hearts for Jose Mourinho but are also learning to love another Latin coach as Antonio Conte displays the sort of tactical acumen that is steering the club towards the title.

headline.print_headline: Conte Winning Chelsea Hearts and Minds-And Points
